FastPattern.description: 2, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, Failed to get PDO
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]Failed 0x[a-f\d]+ to get PDO for TOS 0x[a-f\d]+\.
^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]Failed a request to device/.+ with status -?\d+!

FastPattern.description: 4, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, Failed to add vlapic page
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]Failed to add vlapic page for vcpu \d+ to physmap: -?\d+\.

FastPattern.description: 5, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, Failed to map PV APIC page
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]Failed to map PV APIC page \d+\.

FastPattern.description: 6, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, No handler for oid
7, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, releasing in-use gnttab entry
8, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, Sleep and retry end RX
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]Sleep and retry end RX ring access\.+

FastPattern.description: 12, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, US Failed connect to WMI
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: \[[A-Z ]+\]\[[A-Z]+\]US: Failed to connect to WMI

FastPattern.description: 13, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, US Failed to query Win32 System
14, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, US WMI features disabled
15, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, XENVBD UNKNOWN XSCSI SRB
18, ServiceWarning: HVMXEN, qemu drive out of range
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ HVMXEN-[-a-f\d]+[]\d[]*: qemu: drive `.+' out of range
^\d+ [-\w.]+ iscsid[]\d[]*: Nop-out timedout after \d+ seconds on connection

FastFormatter.condition: Nop-out timedout after (\d+) seconds on connection (\d+:\d+).*
FastFormatter.format: Nop-out timeout after $6 seconds on connection $7

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ multipathd[]\d[]*: checker failed path \d+:\d+ in map [a-f\d]+

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+) ([-\w]+)[]\d[]*: (\[.+\]) Session.create trackid=([a-f\d]+) pool=(\w+) uname=(\S*) is_local_superuser=(\w+) auth_user_sid=(\S*)
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[.+\] Session.create trackid=[a-f\d]+ pool=\w+ uname=\S* is_local_superuser=\w+ auth_user_sid=\S*

FastPattern.description: 36, UserLogonFailure: xapi, Failed to locally authenticate user
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[.+\] Failed to locally authenticate user \S+:
^\d+ [-\w.]+ ovs-vswitchd: \d+\|\w+\|\w+\|[\w ]+: shift \d+kB of load \(with hash \d+\) from [-\w.]+ to [-\w.]+ \(now carrying \d+kB and \d+kB load, respectively\)
^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|audit\] VM.get_allowed_VBD_devices: VM = '[-a-f\d]+ \(Control domain on host: [-\w.]+\)'
^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|console\] Connected; running proxy \(between fds: \d+ and \d+\)

FastPattern.description: 44, ServiceInfo: xapi, console, VM console port
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|console\] VM OpaqueRef:[-a-f\d]+ console port: Some \d+
^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|extauth\] using external auth plugin AD
^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|extauth_plugin_ADlikewise\] Created process pid \(FEFork \([\d,]+\)\) for cmd

^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|pool_db_sync\] (?:Finished DB synchronise|finished writing database xml|received request to write out db as xml|sending headers|writing database xml)

FastPattern.description: 50, ServiceInfo: xapi, pool_db_sync, Starting DB synchronise
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|pool_db_sync\] Starting DB synchronise with host OpaqueRef:[-a-f\d]+

FastPattern.description: 52, ServiceInfo: xapi, sm, SM iso sr_scan

^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|stunnel\] get_reusable_stunnel: stunnel cache is empty; creating a fresh connection to [\d.]+:\d+

FastPattern.description: 56, ServiceInfo: xapi, stunnel, stunnel has pidty

FastPattern.description: 61, ServiceInfo: xapi, xenops, Event on VM
62, ServiceInfo: xapi, xenops, xenops event on VM

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|xenops\] xenopsd event: (?:ignoring event for|processing event for|Updating) VM [-a-f\d]+

FastPattern.description: 64, ServiceInfo: xapi, xapi, Automatically scanning SRs

^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|xapi\] revalidating all external sessions in the local host

FastPattern.description: 70, ServiceInfo: xapi, xapi, Scan of SR

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|xmlrpc_client\] stunnel pid: \d+ \(cached = (?:false|true)\) (?:connected to [\d.]+:\d+|returned stunnel to cache)

FastPattern.description: 77, ServiceInfo: xenopsd, xenops, Received an event
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xenopsd: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|xenops\] Received an event on managed VM [-a-f\d]+

FastPattern.description: 80, ServiceInfo: xenopsd, xenops, Task reference events
82, ServiceInfo: xenopsd, xenops, VM not requesting

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ xapi: \[\w+\|[-\w.]+\|\d+[^|]*\|[./:\w ]*\|xapi\] Successful local authentication user .+ from HTTP request from Internet with User-Agent:
